attributes.title: There Are TOO Many Barnacles! | Gmod: TTT
attributes.caption:
This week on Gmod, there is certainly some trouble in terrorist town.  And by trouble I mean barnacles, A LOT OF THEM.  No but for real, there is just so many barnacles in this video.  At first it was funny how many there were, then it got kinda weird how many there were.  By the end of the video it was just downright disturbing how many barnacles started to litter the map.  I'm not sure where they come from or
if I should call somebody about it, but I am VERY concerned about the situation....  Like what is the normal amount of barnacles?  Is there a normal amount even?  If you have ever come in contact with barnacles or think you know what the appropriate amount of barnacles should be for this video, please contact us ASAP.
